### `EKF2_GPS_CTRL` bitmask

| Bit | Value | Name   | Meaning                  |
|-----|-------|--------|--------------------------|
| 0   | 1     | `HPOS` | Longitude / latitude     |
| 1   | 2     | `VPOS` | **Altitude**             |
| 2   | 4     | `VEL`  | 3D velocity              |
| 3   | 8     | `YAW`  | Dual-antenna heading     |

So common values: `1` = lon/lat only; `3` = lon/lat + altitude; `7` = lon/lat + altitude + velocity
(the default).

