## 8. Quick-reference matrix

Reference = baro (`EKF2_HGT_REF = 0`), `EKF2_BARO_CTRL = 1` in all rows.

| Source | `EKF2_GPS_CTRL = 1` (HPOS only) | `EKF2_GPS_CTRL` with `VPOS` (2/3/7) |
|--------|----------------------------------|--------------------------------------|
| **Baro** — fusion active? | yes | yes |
| **Baro** — is reference? | yes | yes |
| **Baro** — bias estimated? | no (frozen, it is the reference) | no (frozen) |
| **Baro** — resets vert. state? | yes (on start / on all-source reset) | yes |
| **GPS height** — fusion active? | **no** (`VPOS` bit clear) | yes |
| **GPS height** — is reference? | n/a | no |
| **GPS height** — bias estimated? | **no** (estimator inactive) | **yes** (vs baro datum) |
| **GPS height** — resets vert. state? | n/a | no (offset only, except all-source reset) |
| **GPS horizontal** (`HPOS`) | yes (separate, `controlGpsFusion`) | yes |

